.name
AngusTitler
.author
Andreas Gunﬂer 
.version
4.0
.description
A program to create videotitles for (e.g.) your holiday films.  It is
possible to scroll 350 lines up the screen.  Of course, the colors, fonts,
fontstyles, border etc. can be changed.  It is also possible to load a
background picture.  This is only a demo-version that is limited to 10
lines, all other options are enabled, even saving and loading.  The full
version can be obtained from the author for $35 US or 45 DM.  
